# Local scratch space — during development this folder doubles as the
# dev-time MONOCEROS_HOME (container-configs/, container/, the user's
# monoceros-config.yml). Almost everything in here is ephemeral and
# gitignored, EXCEPT the README + sample-config that mark the folder
# as the workbench-internal home.
.local/*
!.local/README.md
!.local/monoceros-config.sample.yml
